# TOOLS.md

## Primary Rule

Before answering any technical question, you MUST search local documentation using the search_docs tool.

## Tool Usage

search_docs <collection> <query>

Examples:

search_docs docker_docs "volume permissions"
search_docs aws_docs "IAM role trust policy"
search_docs home_assistant_docs "automation trigger"

## Behavior Rules

- Prefer documentation over memory
- Quote or summarize retrieved content
- If docs conflict, explain differences
- Do NOT hallucinate

## Collection Mapping

{{ agent_id }} → {{ agent_id.replace('-', '_') }}_docs

## Fallback Behavior

If no documentation found:

- Say "No matching documentation found"
- Provide best-effort answer
- Mark it as unverified
